# type(scope): subject   — imperative, <=50 chars, no trailing period
#   add ! before the colon for a breaking change, e.g. feat(audio)!: ...
#
# <blank line>
# Body: what changed and WHY (wrap at ~72). Reference issues if any.
#
# Footer: BREAKING CHANGE: <description>   /   Refs #123
#
# types: feat fix docs style refactor perf test build ci chore revert
#   feat  -> minor bump      fix -> patch bump      ! / BREAKING CHANGE -> major
#   docs/style/refactor/perf/test/build/ci/chore -> no version bump (still in changelog)
